	<div class="posts">
	<a name="106023762091814322">&nbsp;</a><br>
	.&nbsp; The Enterprise Edition of My Yahoo! is for companies to create online access to tools and resources.  The suite includes web-based <i>portlets</i> and is oriented to business users and portal administrators.&nbsp; The product is pre-integrated with leading portal software platforms, and BEA, Oracle, SAP, Sun and TIBCO are mentioned.<br>
