	.&nbsp; Well, here is Portal in the large.  FirstGov is the Portal of the U.S. Government.  It consolidates on-line citizen services, information services, audience-focused material and hot topics.  There are tabs for businesses, for federal employees, and government-to-government.&nbsp; A fair notion of portal.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#106023680953104825">Wednesday, August 06, 2003</a></span></div>
